cmpReviews: very flexible in terms of schedule, fun environment, cultural diversity, excellent benefits packages. Love the free snack and the beer bash and BBQ.Service Now is a good place to work. Depends on what position you are in, but overall a great company to work for. All and all not a bad place to work.very dynamic place to work at, with very limited coordination, more managers than real workers, need a very thick skin layer to keep going, everyday you might be at risk of loosing job, because manager of other stream did not like you.* Productive and fun workplace with ping pong table.* Good perks with lunch provided once a week
